OL,8,GOur final morning film is a kid's
OL,9,Gclassic and if you haven't seen the
OL,10,Goriginal animated version, come join
OL,11,Gus. After encountering an injured
OL,12,Gdragon, Hiccup the viking discovers
OL,13,Gthat their fire-breathing enemies are
OL,14,Gmisunderstood and an unlikely
OL,15,Gfriendship emerges. Great comedy and
OL,16,Gthe cutest darn dragon you've ever
OL,17,Gseen. Presented on an original 35mm
OL,18,Gprint.
